snippet.title: Trailer Alpha Ghost Exorcism Inc.
snippet.description:
Ghost Exorcism Inc is a scary horror game playing alone or in a team of 6 exorcists. Their mission will be to identify paranormal entities and then exorcise them.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1618540/Ghost_Exorcism_Inc/
